'''''Deep''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] belonging to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. The corvette brought engines to the stranded [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] [[Viper (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|''Viper'']] in the [[Delfii system/Legends|Delfii system]].

